WEBVTT

00:18.601 --> 00:20.103
Thanks.

00:20.687 --> 00:22.814
I've made up my mind.

00:24.899 --> 00:26.568
That's enough.

00:26.651 --> 00:29.863
He alone is enough for me!

00:46.129 --> 00:47.797
B-Brother!

00:50.216 --> 00:51.968
I am...

00:52.594 --> 00:58.224
collapsing... breaking...

02:35.530 --> 02:36.698
breaking...

02:44.414 --> 02:45.707
I am collaps...

02:49.919 --> 02:50.962
Ninja Art: Fire Bridge!

03:05.393 --> 03:07.437
Ninja Art: Fire Monk!

03:13.526 --> 03:14.611
This is...

03:16.362 --> 03:17.739
Gabimaru!

03:19.324 --> 03:20.408
Brother!

03:29.083 --> 03:30.251
Huh?

03:30.919 --> 03:32.879
What is this place?

03:32.962 --> 03:35.965
What’s with this vortex?
It’s too dark to see anything.

03:36.466 --> 03:38.384
Where’s the ninja?

03:39.427 --> 03:41.137
Inside the vortex?

03:42.180 --> 03:46.893
I thought we were fighting.
I don't get it.

03:47.477 --> 03:51.397
Looking at this vortex
just makes me irrationally angry.

03:52.523 --> 03:53.900
It’s an eyesore.

03:55.985 --> 03:58.112
It's an eyesore. Outta my way!

03:58.196 --> 04:02.200
I'll kill you! I'll kill you!

04:02.283 --> 04:05.328
I don't get what's going on,
but I'll kill you anyway!

04:05.912 --> 04:09.999
He’s practically reduced to ashes.
Why isn’t he using that Tao thing?

04:10.875 --> 04:13.253
Gabimaru can’t use Tao.

04:14.003 --> 04:17.966
He doesn't remember.
His opponent’s Tao is huge.

04:18.049 --> 04:20.510
Gabimaru can’t win.

04:20.593 --> 04:23.346
I can't win like this, but...

04:23.429 --> 04:26.057
I just need to use Ascetic Blaze
one more time, I know it.

04:28.476 --> 04:31.479
Even if I die, someone else
from the village will just take my place.

04:31.562 --> 04:34.148
Obstacles should be removed
as much as they can be.

04:34.232 --> 04:36.526
Killing him here takes priority.

04:37.110 --> 04:38.569
Even over my own life.

04:59.590 --> 05:03.011
Hey, hey, he’s really going to die.
What is he trying to do?

05:03.094 --> 05:05.763
His goal should be
to be declared innocent,

05:05.847 --> 05:07.724
but it's all meaningless if he dies.

05:07.807 --> 05:09.517
The same goes for his opponent.

05:09.600 --> 05:12.020
They’ve both lost sight of themselves.

05:12.729 --> 05:14.897
No... Brother.

05:15.398 --> 05:17.358
What are you going this far for?

05:17.442 --> 05:18.985
For what reason?

05:20.570 --> 05:21.487
No way!

05:22.363 --> 05:24.490
In real combat, you relied
on your brother, didn’t you?

05:24.574 --> 05:26.743
I can tell from that unscarred face.

05:27.368 --> 05:30.371
Is he doing it... for me?

05:30.955 --> 05:32.874
You must be joking, brother!

05:33.458 --> 05:35.126
Because I'm...

05:36.669 --> 05:38.046
I'm not worth...

05:40.673 --> 05:41.841
Brother!

05:45.053 --> 05:46.971
I'll kill you! I'll kill you!

05:48.181 --> 05:50.349
In the way... In the way...

05:50.433 --> 05:53.061
Everything is an enemy except us!

05:53.561 --> 05:55.188
Us...

05:55.813 --> 05:57.899
Me...

05:59.901 --> 06:02.528
Who am I?

06:03.446 --> 06:04.280
Brother.

06:10.661 --> 06:12.580
Brother...

06:17.168 --> 06:18.169
Brother.

06:18.753 --> 06:20.213
I'm sorry.

06:20.296 --> 06:23.674
I thought we were fighting together.

06:24.842 --> 06:26.928
But you were fighting
alone the whole time.

06:28.387 --> 06:31.516
It's because I’m weak,
because I’m unreliable,

06:31.599 --> 06:33.601
that you pushed yourself to this point.

06:34.268 --> 06:36.270
Wake up, brother.

06:37.021 --> 06:39.107
I may be just a part of you,

06:39.190 --> 06:41.567
but you're everything to me.

06:42.693 --> 06:43.945
This is my chance.

06:44.612 --> 06:46.280
I'll burn them both alive!

06:46.364 --> 06:47.865
Gabimaru, no!

06:47.949 --> 06:49.158
Miss, that's dangerous!

06:49.242 --> 06:51.786
He's got no Tao left. He'll die!

06:51.869 --> 06:53.329
Ninja Art!

07:02.630 --> 07:04.090
What is this?

07:05.133 --> 07:06.926
Is that girl doing this?

07:16.269 --> 07:17.228
Brother!

07:17.854 --> 07:19.230
Toma, just wait.

07:24.944 --> 07:26.154
Just wait.

07:29.824 --> 07:32.493
Miss! I don’t know
what’s going on, but stop already!

07:35.079 --> 07:36.122
Miss!

07:41.711 --> 07:43.796
What in the world is happening?

07:43.880 --> 07:46.007
Is this also that Tao thing?

07:51.512 --> 07:54.182
Y-you've gotten bigger! Everything has!

07:54.765 --> 07:56.434
What the hell is going on, idiot?

07:56.517 --> 07:58.227
She's cute, idiot!

07:58.311 --> 07:59.854
Shut up.

07:59.937 --> 08:02.273
We'd know if we dissected her.

08:02.356 --> 08:04.484
You're a true idiot.

08:05.443 --> 08:06.736
Good grief.

08:12.867 --> 08:14.869
Nothing but mysteries.

08:14.952 --> 08:16.871
Someone explain this to me.

08:29.467 --> 08:31.511
Seeing it again in the morning...

08:32.720 --> 08:34.263
It really is strange.

08:36.307 --> 08:38.809
A sound I’ve never heard...

08:38.893 --> 08:40.186
A presence...

08:40.269 --> 08:42.980
Either demons lurk here,
or evil manifests.

08:43.064 --> 08:46.859
If all of this island’s mystery
is just an illusion,

08:46.943 --> 08:50.363
then the question is who made
something like this, and how?

08:52.823 --> 08:53.950
Let’s go.

08:58.037 --> 09:00.122
A testing ground for life...

09:00.873 --> 09:02.583
A manufactured island...

09:03.209 --> 09:06.879
I’d be lying if I said
nothing came to mind.

09:07.380 --> 09:10.383
A sense of wrongness
hangs over the entire island.

09:16.430 --> 09:17.848
But...

09:18.474 --> 09:21.227
humans who kill the Tensen...

09:22.270 --> 09:25.773
They will undoubtedly change the island.

09:27.483 --> 09:31.279
Will I still be myself
by the time that happens?

09:43.791 --> 09:44.709
Oh?

09:46.794 --> 09:48.629
Sagi! Shio!

09:48.713 --> 09:49.714
Fuchi-dono.

09:49.797 --> 09:53.467
And... Gabimaru! Those wounds...

09:53.551 --> 09:56.470
Huh? Toma. What?

09:56.554 --> 10:00.600
Huh? And the others?
Where are Ten and Sen?

10:01.350 --> 10:03.352
And what’s with everyone’s clothes?

10:04.020 --> 10:05.438
Uh...

10:05.938 --> 10:07.398
- What happened to you?
- What happened to you?

10:07.982 --> 10:10.401
Mei, did you use your power?

10:11.319 --> 10:13.654
Whoa, it talked! What is that creature?

10:13.738 --> 10:16.657
I must thank you.

10:16.741 --> 10:19.535
To be able to reunite
with this child alive...

10:19.619 --> 10:23.456
Did you come from the ravine?
That was the Soshins' nest, wasn’t it?

10:23.539 --> 10:26.667
You mean the monsters? I killed them all.

10:26.751 --> 10:29.587
Is that a Doshi? You beat it?

10:29.670 --> 10:31.547
Well, yes.

10:31.631 --> 10:33.382
There were about two more as well.

10:33.466 --> 10:35.468
Why can it talk with just a head?

10:36.844 --> 10:38.471
In a thousand years,

10:39.555 --> 10:41.349
this is the first time
I’ve seen people like these.

10:41.932 --> 10:44.852
Killing Soshins, killing Doshis.

10:45.436 --> 10:47.021
Even killing gods.

10:50.524 --> 10:54.070
What they bring to the island may not be

10:54.153 --> 10:56.489
just change alone.

11:06.332 --> 11:08.959
At first, I absolutely
hated the idea, but...

11:09.043 --> 11:10.795
The brain is annoying, but cool.

11:10.878 --> 11:13.756
- It makes sense the more I listen.
- Still, the liver's the best part.

11:13.839 --> 11:16.509
- No, it’s been weird the whole time.
- Anyway, it's cute.

11:16.592 --> 11:17.718
Dumplings.

11:20.096 --> 11:21.013
I see.

11:21.764 --> 11:23.766
So, only eight survived.

11:23.849 --> 11:26.018
Less than half of the landing party.

11:26.102 --> 11:28.729
The woman with a nice ass survived, huh?

11:28.813 --> 11:30.898
Yeah. Super awesome, right?

11:31.482 --> 11:35.194
We should evacuate somewhere away
from the castle as soon as possible, but...

11:35.277 --> 11:38.239
Gabimaru isn't in any state to walk.

11:38.322 --> 11:39.156
And...

11:39.949 --> 11:41.659
Mei...

11:51.752 --> 11:52.670
Still,

11:53.254 --> 11:55.923
so many dead in just three days.

11:56.424 --> 11:58.759
Even if it was an order, it hurts.

12:00.261 --> 12:02.304
What pointless sentimentality.

12:02.388 --> 12:05.433
We were killing each other
until only one remained from the start.

12:05.516 --> 12:09.186
Did you really think you’d all get along
and go home together?

12:10.896 --> 12:13.065
I seriously did.

12:14.358 --> 12:16.068
Is that one your buddy too?

12:16.152 --> 12:18.696
He’s a "worm inside the body," you know?

12:18.779 --> 12:21.031
I spared his life,

12:21.115 --> 12:23.325
and yet he won’t talk, just drags us down.

12:23.409 --> 12:25.786
If he’s a problem for you,
want me to cut him down?

12:26.662 --> 12:28.080
- Stop it.
- Huh?

12:28.164 --> 12:30.958
He may have his reasons.

12:31.041 --> 12:34.336
More importantly, I won't let
anyone else die on my watch.

12:35.838 --> 12:37.840
Unless they’re trying to kill us.

12:37.923 --> 12:42.094
Oh? So there's more to you
than just your big chest.

12:44.096 --> 12:46.098
Sorry to interrupt, but...

12:46.182 --> 12:48.517
Is it really okay to leave Gabimaru
like this?

12:48.601 --> 12:50.352
He’s basically on death’s door.

12:50.436 --> 12:52.229
Oh... Yes...

12:52.313 --> 12:54.106
We need to treat him somewhere fast.

12:54.690 --> 12:57.234
He’s so badly injured,
he lost consciousness.

12:57.318 --> 12:59.737
No, that’s not because of the wounds.

12:59.820 --> 13:02.114
He went berserk, so I punched him.

13:03.908 --> 13:05.493
He is certainly in a bad state.

13:05.576 --> 13:08.037
He must have used too much Tao.

13:08.120 --> 13:09.497
He looks like he could
fade away any moment.

13:10.122 --> 13:12.291
We did everything we could,

13:12.374 --> 13:14.502
but the wounds wouldn’t close at all.

13:14.585 --> 13:15.503
Fuchi-dono.

13:15.586 --> 13:19.089
It's as though it's not just his body,
but something more.

13:19.590 --> 13:22.259
Like the core of him
as a living being was damaged.

13:23.010 --> 13:24.011
No.

13:26.639 --> 13:27.473
Gabimaru!

13:27.556 --> 13:29.350
Hey, don’t push yourself. Stay down.

13:30.351 --> 13:32.102
My strength hasn't returned yet.

13:32.186 --> 13:35.940
There are more unfamiliar faces too.
I need to grasp the situation first.

13:37.191 --> 13:39.735
You're right. Let's rest for a bit.

13:39.818 --> 13:42.154
How are your injuries?

13:43.155 --> 13:45.074
I’m fine. Leave me alone.

13:46.784 --> 13:49.078
You’re still as cold a man as ever.

13:49.662 --> 13:52.831
Those aren't the kind of injuries
you can just leave on their own to heal.

13:52.915 --> 13:54.041
You could die if you're careless.

13:55.709 --> 13:57.044
I don’t care.

13:59.255 --> 14:01.799
Who are you?

14:01.882 --> 14:02.800
Huh?

14:04.718 --> 14:07.429
You know me. I’m Gabimaru of the Hollow.

14:09.306 --> 14:10.432
I thought so.

14:16.647 --> 14:19.400
Sagi, what’s going on?

14:19.483 --> 14:20.317
It must be

14:20.985 --> 14:24.154
that his memories are scrambled
due to abnormal Tao.

14:24.238 --> 14:27.116
He's not the man I know right now.

14:29.910 --> 14:33.706
Yeah. His soul is severely worn down.

14:34.290 --> 14:36.375
Knowing you,

14:36.458 --> 14:38.711
you kept fighting even when we were apart.

14:38.794 --> 14:40.963
Fighting and fighting.

14:41.046 --> 14:44.216
Even when you fell,
you crawled back up, never resting.

14:44.842 --> 14:46.927
All for one purpose.

14:48.304 --> 14:49.388
Sagiri.

14:49.471 --> 14:51.223
Leave this to me.

14:51.307 --> 14:54.226
What should I do? Kill her? But...

14:54.810 --> 14:58.606
Why does looking
at this woman disturb my heart?

14:58.689 --> 15:00.482
Tell me, Gabimaru.

15:00.566 --> 15:02.610
Do you understand why you’re here?

15:04.278 --> 15:06.530
You’ve lost your memories.

15:06.614 --> 15:10.117
But with compatible Tao interference,
you may be able to recover.

15:10.618 --> 15:12.328
Let’s try that first.

15:12.828 --> 15:16.206
Don’t be on guard. I’m not your enemy.

15:16.290 --> 15:17.499
I am...

15:19.335 --> 15:22.838
I am an executioner, not your ally.

15:22.922 --> 15:25.799
What is Gabimaru to you?

15:26.383 --> 15:27.426
I...

15:31.138 --> 15:35.184
I am your precious companion.

15:35.267 --> 15:37.811
So, please, trust me.

15:38.395 --> 15:40.189
Come here--

15:41.398 --> 15:42.858
Don't be on guard--

15:44.318 --> 15:45.277
It’s okay--

15:45.778 --> 15:46.946
Come on, Ga--

15:48.280 --> 15:49.657
Enough already!

15:53.035 --> 15:55.788
It really does seem he used too much Tao.

15:55.871 --> 15:57.831
She's strong!

15:57.915 --> 16:00.876
I said "precious companion,"

16:00.960 --> 16:03.087
but it doesn’t feel right at all.

16:03.170 --> 16:05.714
You and I don’t have
such a soft relationship.

16:06.799 --> 16:09.301
Let’s skip the awkward kindness.

16:09.385 --> 16:12.221
Right now, I just need your strength.

16:12.304 --> 16:14.306
If you don’t like it,
try pushing me away yourself.

16:14.390 --> 16:15.224
Wha...

16:16.308 --> 16:17.476
Between stillness and fury!

16:20.980 --> 16:23.190
You’re not putting any strength into it.

16:23.774 --> 16:26.026
This feels like payback
for something from long ago.

16:26.527 --> 16:28.696
Shall we keep going a bit longer?

16:29.446 --> 16:32.700
What are they doing over there?
Some kind of bedchamber art?

16:32.783 --> 16:33.867
Of course not.

16:33.951 --> 16:37.204
No, but it kind of looks like it.

16:37.788 --> 16:42.209
Through contact,
Tao is circulating and recovering.

16:42.292 --> 16:44.878
Didn’t know Sagirin had that side to her.

16:44.962 --> 16:46.213
I’m surprised too.

16:46.797 --> 16:48.465
But that presence...

16:49.049 --> 16:50.843
Their Tao compatibility is good.

16:50.926 --> 16:53.053
There must be parts of me
I don’t even know

16:53.137 --> 16:54.847
that are compatible like that.

16:55.431 --> 16:57.975
What is this feeling?

16:58.058 --> 16:59.977
It’s like my strength is coming back.

17:00.686 --> 17:03.355
If we all want to return home,
we have to work together.

17:03.939 --> 17:04.857
And...

17:05.774 --> 17:06.608
And...

17:08.861 --> 17:11.196
There’s someone you need
to reunite with, right?

17:30.507 --> 17:32.968
I was consumed by Tao.

17:33.052 --> 17:34.970
I lost myself.

17:35.054 --> 17:37.890
A dangerous power beyond understanding.

17:39.516 --> 17:43.312
Dangerous, but if you master it,
you’re unstoppable.

17:47.191 --> 17:48.692
Just wait.

17:52.279 --> 17:54.698
Comes at me in droves, huh?

17:54.782 --> 17:55.699
Well...

17:55.783 --> 17:57.701
Perfect practice for Tao, right?

17:58.619 --> 17:59.953
Hey, you guys!

18:00.037 --> 18:02.956
Bet your meat tastes good, huh?

18:06.043 --> 18:07.086
It’s cramped,

18:07.669 --> 18:09.713
but this should hide us from the monsters.

18:10.380 --> 18:13.467
Perfect, right? I found it myself.

18:13.550 --> 18:14.718
We can’t let our guard down.

18:15.719 --> 18:18.222
The Tensen perceive more
than just with their eyes.

18:18.305 --> 18:19.973
You’re a coward, huh?

18:20.057 --> 18:22.226
That scared of these so-called Tensen?

18:22.309 --> 18:24.144
Ignorance is bliss.

18:24.228 --> 18:25.270
Huh?

18:25.354 --> 18:26.480
Of course I’m scared.

18:26.563 --> 18:28.982
No matter how much you cut them,
they won’t die.

18:29.566 --> 18:32.486
It took five of us
just to kill one of those monsters.

18:33.070 --> 18:35.489
Since we caused that much
commotion in their territory,

18:35.572 --> 18:37.741
the others will notice sooner or later.

18:38.826 --> 18:41.245
You’ve met them too, haven’t you?

18:41.328 --> 18:42.704
Gabimaru.

18:43.205 --> 18:46.125
Yeah. At the gate.

18:46.208 --> 18:49.128
Your memories have returned.

18:50.254 --> 18:52.131
Only little by little.

18:53.799 --> 18:56.760
Sorry for all that trouble.

18:58.095 --> 19:00.973
But thanks to that, it really sank in.

19:01.056 --> 19:03.851
The power of Tao... its strength...

19:03.934 --> 19:05.102
and the backlash.

19:05.185 --> 19:07.771
And how terrifying
the Tensen who wield it are.

19:07.855 --> 19:10.607
Then shouldn’t we get
off this island right now?

19:10.691 --> 19:13.068
Better than dealing
with something that dangerous.

19:13.152 --> 19:17.030
I think we'd have a better chance
at explaining ourselves to the shogunate.

19:17.614 --> 19:20.325
Just surviving won’t let me see my wife.

19:20.409 --> 19:23.620
Without a pardon guaranteeing
innocence and protection...

19:25.080 --> 19:27.416
Hey, about that...

19:34.131 --> 19:36.300
An illusion? I see.

19:36.884 --> 19:39.720
By showing you an illusion
of a wife who doesn’t exist,

19:39.803 --> 19:41.054
you're made into a puppet.

19:41.722 --> 19:44.558
That’s what the Iwagakure chief
came up with, right?

19:45.142 --> 19:47.936
Well, we’ll know once
we return to the mainland.

19:48.020 --> 19:49.313
My goal hasn’t changed.

19:49.897 --> 19:50.939
Find the elixir.

19:51.023 --> 19:53.442
What? H-hold on a minute!

19:53.525 --> 19:56.570
I’m saying I don’t want to take that risk.

19:56.653 --> 19:58.155
Even if we bring back the elixir,

19:58.238 --> 20:00.199
what’s the point
if your wife doesn’t exist?

20:00.782 --> 20:02.201
She does. Absolutely.

20:02.284 --> 20:03.702
How can you be so sure?

20:03.785 --> 20:05.412
Because I feel it.

20:05.495 --> 20:06.830
Huh? What does that mean?

20:06.914 --> 20:07.956
Yuzuriha.

20:08.040 --> 20:10.709
What? Who benefits
from tiptoeing around this?

20:10.792 --> 20:13.754
It's better for Gabi to force him
to be clear about this.

20:13.837 --> 20:18.175
Gabimaru is usually so logical in battle,
yet he’s vague here.

20:18.258 --> 20:19.593
That’s your answer.

20:20.177 --> 20:21.511
You can’t prove it?

20:25.098 --> 20:26.099
That’s true.

20:26.683 --> 20:30.103
I’m not as good with words as you.

20:30.187 --> 20:31.605
So, I can't say it well.

20:32.314 --> 20:35.359
All I can remember are small details.

20:37.402 --> 20:41.323
Like, her voice.
A little high, slow, and gentle.

20:41.949 --> 20:45.118
That tone... How should I describe it?

20:46.203 --> 20:48.121
Eyes that narrow when she smiles.

20:48.747 --> 20:50.707
Long, soft fingers.

20:51.333 --> 20:53.418
When her hair sways, it smells nice.

20:54.711 --> 20:56.380
When the weather's nice,

20:56.463 --> 20:59.883
sitting on the veranda,
behind the scent of sun and grass,

21:00.467 --> 21:02.052
I smell her.

21:08.016 --> 21:09.268
Even now, I do.

21:19.361 --> 21:20.237
Dear.

21:24.241 --> 21:25.158
Yui.

21:26.868 --> 21:28.578
That’s her name.

21:29.288 --> 21:30.163
Yui.

21:30.664 --> 21:34.084
She’s not an illusion. I feel it.

21:34.668 --> 21:38.588
You can ask me to prove it,
but that’s hard. So...

21:39.756 --> 21:42.092
The only way is to leave this island
and see her again.

21:43.176 --> 21:44.594
Yes.

21:45.637 --> 21:47.097
You're right.

21:47.764 --> 21:51.226
So you’re dragging others into this
for the sake of your woman?

21:52.394 --> 21:53.228
My wife.

21:54.813 --> 21:57.691
You’re a real man. I like that.

21:57.774 --> 22:00.444
I'll tag along if I have a free hand
while I'm chasing my own ambitions.

22:01.486 --> 22:03.739
I’m hunting monsters anyway.

22:05.449 --> 22:08.201
He's saying he can do it
with one hand. Nice one.

22:09.703 --> 22:12.914
You're a ninja and you just
exposed your weakness.

22:12.998 --> 22:15.959
- But that may be exactly why.
- Huh?

22:16.043 --> 22:19.546
While he was talking,
his Tao surged strongly.

22:19.629 --> 22:22.632
For him, that weakness and strength
might be two sides of the same coin.

22:23.550 --> 22:27.220
That tiny body holds
an absurd amount of Tao.

22:27.804 --> 22:31.475
Those who have something
to lose are strong.

22:43.403 --> 22:45.363
Weaklings taste bad.

22:45.447 --> 22:46.990
That’s rare.

22:48.950 --> 22:51.328
A mixed breed.

22:51.411 --> 22:55.248
Were you the one who killed Mu Dan?

24:22.961 --> 24:25.964
Subtitle translation by: Maslin Friedman
